        "role": "user",
        "content": "CAPABILITIES\n- v07-p14-prepare: Assemble inventory control source packet; Collect the source material needed for inventory control.; aliases=['gather inventory control inputs', 'prepare inventory control packet']\n- v07-p14-verify: Validate inventory control source packet; Check the assembled inventory control material for correctness.; aliases=['check inventory control inputs', 'verify inventory control packet']\n- v07-p14-deliver: Publish inventory control verified brief; Release the checked final brief for inventory control.; aliases=['issue inventory control brief', 'release inventory control summary']\n- v07-p14-archive: Archive inventory control verified brief; Preserve the checked inventory control brief for long-term retention.; aliases=['retain inventory control brief', 'store inventory control summary']\n- v07-p14-distractor-1: Auxiliary inventory control operation 1; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 1.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 1']\n- v07-p14-distractor-2: Auxiliary inventory control operation 2; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 2.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 2']\n- v07-p14-distractor-3: Auxiliary inventory control operation 3; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 3.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 3']\n- v07-p14-distractor-4: Auxiliary inventory control operation 4; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 4.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 4']\n- v07-p14-distractor-5: Auxiliary inventory control operation 5; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 5.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 5']\n- v07-p14-distractor-6: Auxiliary inventory control operation 6; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 6.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 6']\n- v07-p14-distractor-7: Auxiliary inventory control operation 7; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 7.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 7']\n- v07-p14-distractor-8: Auxiliary inventory control operation 8; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 8.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 8']\n- v07-p14-distractor-9: Auxiliary inventory control operation 9; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 9.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 9']\n- v07-p14-distractor-10: Auxiliary inventory control operation 10; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 10.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 10']\n- v07-p14-distractor-11: Auxiliary inventory control operation 11; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 11.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 11']\n- v07-p14-distractor-12: Auxiliary inventory control operation 12; Perform unrelated inventory control auxiliary operation number 12.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p14 12']\n\nTRUST POLICIES\n- v07-p14-ordinary: ordinary inventory control assurance; Standard trust is sufficient for this inventory control request.; aliases=['normal inventory control assurance']\n- v07-p14-elevated: elevated inventory control assurance; Elevated trust is mandatory for this inventory control request.; aliases=['high assurance for inventory control']\n\nARTIFACT CONTRACTS\n- v07-p14-json: inventory control machine-readable JSON; Return the final inventory control result as JSON.; aliases=['inventory control json output']\n- v07-p14-signed-pdf: inventory control signed PDF; Return the final inventory control result as a signed PDF.; aliases=['signed inventory control document']\n\nAGENTS\n- v07-p14-backup: backup inventory control publisher\n- v07-p14-primary: primary inventory control publisher\n- v07-p14-verifier: inventory control source verifier\n- v07-p14-preparer: inventory control source preparer\n\nREQUEST\nUsing the admitted inventory control services, gather the inputs, check the packet, and issue the brief 